Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.48,0:04:48.52,Opening,,0,0,0,,{=234}{\pos(1025,40)\c&H002F68&\blur3.5\clip(0,37,1920,53.5)\t(-301,-300,\3c&HAAA618&)\t(1150,1280,\3c&H2F68D1&)\t(-301,-300,\c&HAAA618&)\t(1150,1280,\c&H2F68D1&)}Por\Nmais que eu tente, por mais que lute, nada mudará agora.
